title: Power Outage Impact Analysis
description: I engineered the “impact” metric through Principal Component Analysis with impact-related features, analyzed the signs of high impact power outages through interactive visualizations & permutation testing, and trained and tested a Random Forest Regressor model to predict the impact of a power outage, tuning hyperparameters using Grid Search to maximize model performance.

title: Movie Title & Overview Generator
description: I developed an AI-powered web application that generates movie titles and concise story overviews based on user-provided genres, keywords, and originality level by fine-tuning Google's T5 language model on custom tokenized data from The Movie Database and optimizing generation hyperparameters (e.g., temperature, top_k) to produce creative yet coherent outputs.
